  ID: MenAtArms
  Name: Elias
  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  Description: "Wound: Both legs shattered by cannon shot, splinters of bone embedded
    in flesh.\n\nStory: Elias, a German mercenary, lies motionless except for his
    trembling hands. His eyes, wide and glassy, stare into the sky as he mutters
    about a daughter in Augsburg who will never see him return. His voice breaks
    as he begs you \u2014 not for healing \u2014 but to not let him die alone, like
    so many nameless corpses left in the dirt.\n\n\nRequired bandages to heal: 3"
  slotNumber: 1
  requiredResource: Bandage
  requiredAmount: 3
